OL,3,CSchools forced to close as burst pipe
OL,4,Cleaves homes and businesses without
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FSchools in Oxford have been forced to
OL,8,Fclose after a burst pipe left homes
OL,9,Fand businesses without water.
OL,11,FPeople in the OX3, OX4 and OX33 areas
OL,12,Fwere left with either low pressure or
OL,13,Fno supply after a pipe burst on Mill
OL,14,FLane near Headington.
OL,16,FThames Water said engineers have
OL,17,Fworked through the night to repair the
OL,18,Fpipe, but that a bottled water station
OL,19,Fhas been opened at Oxford Thornhill
OL,20,FPark and Ride for those still affected.
