OL,7,FA number of schools have been closed
OL,8,Fas a result of the issue, including
OL,9,FHeadington Quarry Nursery School, New
OL,10,FMarston Primary School and The Swan
OL,11,FSchool.
OL,13,FA Thames Water spokesperson said: "Our
OL,14,Fspecialist team worked through the
OL,15,Fnight to repair a burst pipe on Mill
OL,16,FLane, OX3, which means all customers
OL,17,Fshould now have water.
OL,19,F"We will continue to carry out
OL,20,Fessential work around the repair today.
