OL,7,F"This could see some low pressures
OL,8,Facross the network which may impact
OL,9,Fsome customers. We apologise for the
OL,10,Finconvenience and understand that it's
OL,11,Ffrustrating when your tap water isn't
OL,12,Fflowing properly.
OL,14,F"To enable this continued work,
OL,15,Ftraffic management will be in place on
OL,16,Fthe A40, which may cause traffic
OL,17,Fdisruption.
