OL,7,F"We have also opened a Bottled Water
OL,8,FStation which can be used in case of
OL,9,Fany disruption to water supply. The
OL,10,Fstation at Oxford Thornhill Park &
OL,11,FRide, London Rd, Headington, Oxford
OL,12,FOX3 8DP will open at 09:00am.
OL,14,F"We understand how disruptive this can
OL,15,Fbe, and we're doing everything we can
OL,16,Fto resolve the issue and get water
OL,17,Fflowing again as quickly as possible.
OL,18,FWe'll provide an update on our
OL,19,Fprogress tomorrow morning.
